{
  "message": "\ud83c\udfa8 docs: ACMM badge uses KubeStellar globe-and-star logo\n\nReplaces the GitHub icon with a tiny inline SVG silhouette of the\nKubeStellar Console logo (globe with meridians + 5-point star) by\npassing &logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,... on the shields.io URL.\nThis overrides the namedLogo:github returned by the Netlify badge\nfunction (per shields.io endpoint precedence rules \u2014 explicit query\nparams win over endpoint output).\n\nTiny silhouette (490 bytes raw, 466 bytes base64) instead of the\nfull kubestellar-logo.svg (728-line PNG-wrapped-in-SVG, way over\nshields.io's data-URI size limit). Bumped &v=3 to bust GitHub camo\ncache from the previous badge URL.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
